text: Trigonopterus nitidulus is a species of flightless weevil in the genus Trigonopterus from Indonesia. == Description == Trigonopterus nitidulus was described in a journal in March 2019. It is native to Indonesia. == References == Category:Beetles described in 2019 Category:Insects of Indonesia nitidulus Category:Beetles of Asia Category:Endemic fauna of Indonesia Category:Trigonopterus stubs
